author: MIKE PESCARO
title: Trump to Speak at Mass. Elementary School
text: The latest news from around the state Donald Trump to Speak at Massachusetts Elementary School Republican Donald Trump will be speaking at an elementary school in Massachusetts next week. The presidential candidate will address a crowd at Tyngsborough Elmentary School on Friday, Oct. 16. The doors will open at 5 p.m. Tickets are free and can be ordered here . Published at 4:46 PM EDT on Oct 9, 2015
